content: denizekiz: Contributed several important fixes this month, merging 5 PRs that addressed configuration issues and technical limitations, including adding Claude Vertex configs (#330, +23/-0 lines) and fixing compute unit settings (#276). Reported two issues that were subsequently closed (#379 and #679), with sporadic activity concentrated on a few days. Most changes were small but impactful, primarily focusing on code modifications with some documentation improvements, such as updating the README with WSL 2 link information (#419).
